  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/9165a617045249671dda05791d3462d0.avif?t=1773953536\" width=620 height=150 /></span></p></p><br><h1>EARLY ACCESS</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/d845978674c5324a88a8ec9df0643f17.avif?t=1773953536\" width=620 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good people at Valve once said players should buy into an early access for what it is now and not for what it could be. We agree! Make sure you read the <strong>Early Access Game</strong> section above.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hard Chip is in its active development phase. While the core player experience is in place, the content is subject to change. You may encounter areas where fine-tuning is ongoing, and some features may evolve as we continue to improve the game. Your feedback is invaluable in helping us shape the final product, and we appreciate your understanding and support during this exciting phase of development!</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Step into the shoes of 'new_user', an engineer tasked with the monumental challenge of repairing machines to escape from an unknown location. Your tool? The fundamental building blocks of digital logic: complementary transistors.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD YOUR OWN PARTS</h2>Begin with the basics of electronic components, creating gates out of complementary transistors. Learn the art of electronic design as you progress from simple NAND and NOR gates to complex circuits capable of performing intricate tasks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/2936315de35b696b128e3181ee11c83f.poster.avif?t=1773953536\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/2936315de35b696b128e3181ee11c83f.webm?t=1773953536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/2936315de35b696b128e3181ee11c83f.mp4?t=1773953536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ASSEMBLE THEM</h2>Combine your gates into larger, more sophisticated parts. Each assembly is a puzzle, demanding not just intelligence but creativity, planning, and foresight.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/6f54d5d7dffb1e802f7239028ed49d56.poster.avif?t=1773953536\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/6f54d5d7dffb1e802f7239028ed49d56.webm?t=1773953536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/6f54d5d7dffb1e802f7239028ed49d56.mp4?t=1773953536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OPTIMIZE</h2>Optimize your designs for efficiency and space, pushing the limits of your engineering prowess.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/b549df69f4476bdf945c4c3c2caab4ef.poster.avif?t=1773953536\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/b549df69f4476bdf945c4c3c2caab4ef.webm?t=1773953536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/b549df69f4476bdf945c4c3c2caab4ef.mp4?t=1773953536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TERMINALS</h2>All electronics seem non-functional, and they are your only way forward.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/cfbf2edc11a2c728ca23a5ec6f836470.poster.avif?t=1773953536\" width=620 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/cfbf2edc11a2c728ca23a5ec6f836470.webm?t=1773953536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/cfbf2edc11a2c728ca23a5ec6f836470.mp4?t=1773953536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIND YOUR WAY OUT</h2>Advance into a strange world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/00a062ad53720f617b681c188b008eb5.avif?t=1773953536\" width=620 height=302 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Step into the shoes of 'new_user', an engineer tasked with the monumental challenge of repairing machines to escape from an unknown location. Your tool? The fundamental building blocks of digital logic: complementary transistors.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD YOUR OWN PARTS</h2>Begin with the basics of electronic components, creating gates out of complementary transistors. Learn the art of electronic design as you progress from simple NAND and NOR gates to complex circuits capable of performing intricate tasks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/2936315de35b696b128e3181ee11c83f.poster.avif?t=1773953536\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/2936315de35b696b128e3181ee11c83f.webm?t=1773953536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/2936315de35b696b128e3181ee11c83f.mp4?t=1773953536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ASSEMBLE THEM</h2>Combine your gates into larger, more sophisticated parts. Each assembly is a puzzle, demanding not just intelligence but creativity, planning, and foresight.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/6f54d5d7dffb1e802f7239028ed49d56.poster.avif?t=1773953536\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/6f54d5d7dffb1e802f7239028ed49d56.webm?t=1773953536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/6f54d5d7dffb1e802f7239028ed49d56.mp4?t=1773953536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OPTIMIZE</h2>Optimize your designs for efficiency and space, pushing the limits of your engineering prowess.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/b549df69f4476bdf945c4c3c2caab4ef.poster.avif?t=1773953536\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/b549df69f4476bdf945c4c3c2caab4ef.webm?t=1773953536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/b549df69f4476bdf945c4c3c2caab4ef.mp4?t=1773953536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TERMINALS</h2>All electronics seem non-functional, and they are your only way forward.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/cfbf2edc11a2c728ca23a5ec6f836470.poster.avif?t=1773953536\" width=620 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/cfbf2edc11a2c728ca23a5ec6f836470.webm?t=1773953536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/cfbf2edc11a2c728ca23a5ec6f836470.mp4?t=1773953536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIND YOUR WAY OUT</h2>Advance into a strange world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844290/extras/00a062ad53720f617b681c188b008eb5.avif?t=1773953536\" width=620 height=302 /></span>",
